infoTooltip:
Connect to a new remote Docker daemon.
If the HTTP connection is selected, only host and post fields will be considered.
The remaining fileds are used for a mutual HTTPS connection.
For more informations on the other fields, see the README.md
hostInfoTooltip:
Host name of the remote machine running the Docker daemon.
Can be an IP address.
portInfoTooltip: Port the Docker daemon will listen to. Defaults to 2375.
